span.p: My personal style, which I (Ste) am going to recommend to you is to start out with finding ways to make this tutorial game your own.

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p: Expand it with some new ideas and find other tutorials that kinda fit where you want to go with it, but don't just follow 1:1 - chop multiple tutorials apart and build your first Frankenstein game!

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p: Then try the same style with a new project, maybe join a game jam, they can be lots of fun too. Stay curios and you will find your own way. Good luck on your journey!
